                     "mule, and bring him down to Gihon.\n"
                     "Let Zadok the priest and Nathan the prophet anoint him "
                     "there king over Israel. Blow the trumpet, and say, 'Long "
                     "live king Solomon!'\n"
                     "Then come up after him, and he shall come and sit on my "
