                    "multiplied, and grew very mighty.\n"
                    "Because the midwives feared God, he gave them families.\n"
                    "Pharaoh commanded all his people, saying, 'You shall cast "
                    "every son who is born into the river, and every daughter "
                    "you shall save alive.'\n"
                    "Yahweh spoke to Moses, saying,\n"
                    "'On the first day of the first month you shall raise up "
                    "the tabernacle of the Tent of Meeting.\n"
                    "You shall put the ark of the testimony in it, and you "
                    "shall screen the ark with the veil.\n"
                    "You shall bring in the table, and set in order the things "
