                    "He brought the ark into the tabernacle, and set up the "
                    "veil of the screen, and screened the ark of the "
                    "testimony, as Yahweh commanded Moses.\n"
                    "He put the table in the Tent of Meeting, on the side of "
                    "the tabernacle northward, outside of the veil.\n"
                    "He set the bread in order on it before Yahweh, as Yahweh "
                    "commanded Moses.\n"
                    "He put the lamp stand in the Tent of Meeting, opposite "
