                    "He put up the screen of the door to the tabernacle.\n"
                    "He set the altar of burnt offering at the door of the "
                    "tabernacle of the Tent of Meeting, and offered on it the "
                    "burnt offering and the meal offering, as Yahweh commanded "
                    "Moses.\n"
                    "He set the basin between the Tent of Meeting and the "
                    "altar, and put water therein, with which to wash.\n"
                    "Moses, Aaron, and his sons washed their hands and their "
