                 "and he will renounce you to your face.'\n"
                 "Yahweh said to Satan, 'Behold, all that he has is in your "
                 "power. Only on himself don't stretch out your hand.'\n"
                 "So Satan went out from the presence of Yahweh.\n"
                 "It fell on a day when his sons and his daughters were eating "
                 "and drinking wine in their oldest brother's house,\n"
