                    "then you shall make your way prosperous, and then you "
                    "shall have good success.\n"
                    "Haven't I commanded you? Be strong and courageous. Don't "
                    "be afraid. Don't be dismayed, for Yahweh your God is with "
                    "you wherever you go.'\n"
                    "Then Joshua commanded the officers of the people, "
                    "saying,\n"
